manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: What Stupell Industries Has to Offer: Framed Giclée Our giclée prints are carefully mounted on a durable MDF backing, and then perfectly finished in a 1.5 inch thick woodgrain frame. Frame colors include black, gray farmhouse and white. Stretched Canvas Our stretched canvas is created with only the highest standards. We use only the highest quality inks and canvas on our in house Mimaki printers, and then hand cut and stretch each piece over a 1.5 inch thick wooden frame for hanging Wood Plaque All of our wall plaques start off as high quality lithograph prints that are then mounted on durable 0.5 inch thick MDF wood. Each piece is hand finished and comes with a fresh layer of foil on the sides to give it a crisp clean look.

American Made At Stupell Industries we take pride in our American made wall decor. Every piece of wall art in our product line is proudly made in our facilities in Rhode Island. Whether it is a stretched canvas wall art, a wood plaque, or a framed giclee print, it is all made in USA! Stupell Industries About Us: Stupell Industries has been providing quality wall art and decorative accessories for over forty years. Stupell’s products range from canvas wall art, wood wall art, and framed giclée art in a variety of themes, mediums and sizes. No matter the style, our modern, contemporary, traditional, or baby wall art and home decor is crafted with the utmost consideration and care. All of our products are proudly made in the USA, and are brought to life at our facilities in Johnston, RI.
Our Promise: At Stupell Industries, we promise to provide our customers with premium wall décor.
